{"tid":1145273,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"大學出貓真係對於人性嘅一大考驗","createTime":"2019-05-08T14:54:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T15:23:27.000Z","uid":216896,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"86ce72def307829ecb8f3aa435508ecd2d8fda8a","tid":1145273,"uid":216896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T14:54:55.000Z","msg":"比起中學大學真係好撚易出貓<br />\n<br />\n成個幾百個考生個個好似腎虧咁 係咁去廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過又難怪 成個屎坑都冇人 你喺入面做掌上壓都冇人知 尤其是啲貓紙如果係攝得多啲嘅話 嗰啲背書課直情可以滿分<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係早兩日睇咗條話出貓等於呃自己嘅片 我應該會爆咗四<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為咗人格<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我忍<br />\n<br />\n同時強烈譴責嗰啲尿頻嘅撚樣 <br />\n係呀話緊你 回頭是岸呀 gpa可以輸 但係人品唔可以輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ca482f9cb8209a70e5df2f743ad50435161a1f","tid":1145273,"uid":210559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T15:23:27.000Z","msg":"每次都喺度爭扎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完你個post 個人都堅定咗少少<br />\n但到時考可能又呻自己堅持啲無謂嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}